    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Solid fair-condition vehicle that runs and drives, but it is not a showroom car and does show its age. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear, including paint flaws, body blemishes, and normal interior wear from use. This is a practical driver for someone who wants usable transportation at a more affordable price point and is comfortable with an older vehicle that has visible imperfections.",
