    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of potential. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer looking for a low-cost way to get on the road, a practical project, or a work-and-utility car. Priced to reflect its overall condition, it offers strong value for someone who prioritizes budget and opportunity over cosmetics.",
      "price": 4950.0,
