      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right owner? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts conversations for all the right reasons: it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option that could make a handy daily runaround, first car, or project for someone who enjoys getting stuck in. A lot of honest value here for the money, and at this price it\u2019s a great chance to get behind the wheel without breaking the bank.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, usable driver with solid project potential and plenty of mechanical character. It shows its age cosmetically and will need continued sorting, but it starts, runs, and offers a strong foundation for someone who wants an affordable car with good bones. The powertrain feels eager, the chassis is straightforward, and it\u2019s the kind of vehicle that rewards an owner who appreciates simple, serviceable hardware. A great budget entry point for a daily beater, weekend fixer, or parts donor with real usable value left.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way to get on the road. Honest used car with wear, but priced to sell fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with stories in its steel and plenty of road-ready spirit, this one has the kind of honest, lived-in character that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates vintage grit, weekend wrenching, or simply wants an affordable ride with personality you just don\u2019t find in cookie-cutter commuters. Park it in the driveway, put a little vision behind the wheel, and you\u2019ve got something memorable.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle that offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price. This car shows its age and is best suited for buyers who value affordability, simplicity, and a straightforward ownership experience. An excellent opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or someone seeking an inexpensive second vehicle.",
      "price": 4995.0,
