      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car for someone who needs basic transportation or wants a straightforward project. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it still has plenty of usable life for the right buyer. Great option if you\u2019re handy, need an affordable runabout, or want something you can improve over time without spending a fortune. Priced to sell and open to a fair conversation.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Strong-running project with solid bones and plenty of usable life left in the drivetrain. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels planted enough to make this a great budget driver, shop truck, or weekend fixer-upper. Cosmetically it shows its age and it\u2019s not perfect, but for someone who values mechanical substance over polish, this is an honest vehicle with real potential. Priced to move for the next owner who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
